flowchart TD
    A[Source Data] --> B[Split into Chunks]
    B --> C[Create Embeddings]
    C --> D[Store in Vector Database]

    E[User Question] --> F[Retrieve Relevant Chunks]
    D --> F

    F --> G[Send Context + Question to LLM]
    G --> H[Generated Answer]

    H --> I[Evaluate Answer]
    F --> I
